="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 42.75pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p align="center" class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">公共英语&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="61" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 45.75pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">大学语文</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="94" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 70.5pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">设计基础</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="center" class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">注：各专业满&nbsp;30人以上方可开班。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">三、入学考试及免试政策</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">1、考试入学</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;由上海交通大学命题并组织入学测试，择优录取为2011年秋季学生。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(255,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;<font color="#000000">统一入学考试时间：</font><font color="#f73809">2011年8月13日</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(255,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2、单科免试、面试入学政策</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: -20pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 20pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">（一）单科免试</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">(1)持&nbsp;PET3、PRETCO-A、CET4或以上级别证书及改革后CET4考试成绩达到405分的考生可免试入学考试科目&nbsp;&ldquo;公共英语&rdquo;；</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">（2）年满40周岁者可申请免试入学考试科目&ldquo;公共英语&rdquo;。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">（3）持各省或全国计算机等级考试证书者可免试入学考试科目&ldquo;计算机文化基础&rdquo;。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 0.05pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">（二）保送生测试：符合下列条件之一的10、11届大专毕业生，可申请免于笔试，面试入学：（1）符合入学考试&ldquo;公共英语&rdquo;免试条件，且专科阶段各科平均成绩达&nbsp;70分以上者；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">（2）同时符合&ldquo;公共英语&rdquo;和&ldquo;计算机文化基础&rdquo;两门单科免试条件者；</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">（3）报考同类专业，且专科阶段各科平均成绩达75分以上者；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">（4）获得校级以上优秀奖励者；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">（5）达到当年成人高考本科最低控制分数线者；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">（6）获得双专科毕业证书者。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 5pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 12pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 5.05pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">报名时需提交面试入学申请表、获奖证书、英语等级证书、成绩大表等证明材料。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">四、学习期限、学分、学费</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">实行学分制管理，基本修业年限为两年半至五年，一年两学期，每学期按学分缴纳学费。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　英语专业总计９８学分，每学分２００元，每学期按学分缴纳学费；</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　艺术设计专业总计９８学分，每学分２５０元，每学期按学分缴纳学费；</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　其它专业总计９８学分，每学分１８０元，每学期按学分缴纳学费。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">　　</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">五、毕业证书、学位证书</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;学 历教育学生根据有关规定修读完成教学计划规定的学分，成绩合格，通过全国网络教育&nbsp;&ldquo;大学英语&nbsp;&rdquo;及&nbsp;&ldquo;计算机应用基础&nbsp;&rdquo;统一考试，可获得上海交通大学 毕业证书（注明&nbsp;&ldquo;网络教育&nbsp;&rdquo;），由教育部统一电子注册，国家承认；符合学位条例规定条件者，授予上海交通大学成人教育学士学位。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp; <br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">非学历课程进修生</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">１、课程进修生属于非学历教育。凡有能力并自愿参加课程学习的所有人员均可报名参加学习。学历、专业、年龄不限。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">２、课程进修生入学前可参加我院课程进修生入学测试。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">３、课程进修生可根据个人需求选修我院开设的所有课程。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">４、课程进修生按课程管理，申请者每学期必须按规定交纳所修学分的学费，收费标准与学历教育相同。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">５、课程进修生在取得学历教育资格后，课程进修期间所获学分及课程成绩，可按学院规定申请转入学历教育。最短修业年限自取得学历教育资格后开始计算。</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">奖学金制度</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">学院2011年拨款100万元作为奖学金，分别设立&ldquo;新生奖学金&rdquo;、&ldquo;卓越奖学金&rdquo;和&ldquo;优秀奖学金&rdquo;三类奖项。以鼓励广大学生刻苦学习，自强不息。奖励名额不低于在籍学生的10%，对于成绩突出的学生予以减免学费的高额奖励。奖学金申请网址&nbsp;</span><span><a href="http://scholarship.onlinesjtu.com/"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">http://scholarship.onlinesjtu.com</span></a></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 14.75pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">报名方法</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">1、报名需备：</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">（1）本人身份证原件及国民教育系列相应证书原件及复印件，应届毕业生需携带学生证；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">（2）符合科目免试条件者需携带相关证书原件及复印件一份；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">（3）报名时缴纳报名考务费共92元（艺术设计专业报名考务费144元）&nbsp;，报名后一律不退款。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align="center">\r\n<table align="center" style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-table-layout-alt: fixed">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style="HEIGHT: 14.25pt">\r\n            <td width="69" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 52.4pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="116" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 87.35pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="138" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(