ottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width="133" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 100.45pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p align="center" class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="center" class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">特别提示</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">◆考生户籍所在地不限，不转户口，不调档案，不享受国家补贴等全日制学生待遇，学院不提供、安排、介绍住宿。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">◆学校将在入学时、学习期间、毕业前多次查验学生的国民教育系列毕业证书及电子注册号，凡持不符合条件的证书或假证报名者，一切后果均自负。一经发现，学校有权取消其报名、学习、毕业资格，且不退还学费。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">◆</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(255,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">学院招生政策包括毕业证书、学位证书颁发以国家现行政策为准，若国家政策调整，即按新政策执行。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(255,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span></p>', 3, 1, '2011-08-15 11:50:57');
INSERT INTO `mbnews` (`nid`, `nclass`, `s_name`, `ntitle`, `ncon`, `nclick`, `nbool`, `ndate`) VALUES
(173, 6, '江南大学', '舞台美术设计方向招生标准、学费及考试科目', '<p><img width="750" height="196" alt="" src="/userfiles/image/a2.jpg" /></p>', 12, 1, '2011-08-26 11:45:26'),
(174, 6, '江南大学', '戏剧影视表演方向招生计划、学费及考试科目', '<p><img src="/userfiles/image/a3.jpg" alt="" /></p>', 13, 1, '2011-08-26 11:46:55'),
(175, 5, '江南大学', '学院组织清明扫墓，艺术教育积极参与', '<p>2011年3月30日，继网学院团委学生会组织学生前往无锡烈士陵园清明扫墓，艺术教育中心学生积极参与，感受无锡烈士风采，怀念革命先驱。此次活动提高了学生的思想教育、培养了爱国精神，具有重大意义！</p>\r\n<p><img width="653" height="492" src="http://www.jnuae.cn/userfiles/image/%E6%9C%AA%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D4.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p><img src="http://www.jnuae.cn/userfiles/image/%E6%9C%AA%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D5.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p><img width="651" height="487" src="http://www.jnuae.cn/userfiles/image/%E6%9C%AA%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D6.jpg" alt="" /></p>', 2, 1, '2011-08-26 13:58:45'),
(176, 5, '江南大学', '2010级戏剧影视表演年度汇报演出', '<p>2010级戏剧影视表演年度汇报演出，参加人员：2010级戏剧影视表演班学生，指导老师：才华</p>\r\n<p>2010-2011学年第一学期期末表演班话剧汇报演出于10年12月底在艺术教育中心小剧场举行，表演班全体师生积极参与，为大家展现了话剧《雷 雨》片段和现代剧《白日梦》的汇报演出，得到学院领导和相关嘉宾的一致好评，此次汇报演出对推进表演教学质量和学生专业知识的提升起到了很大的作用。</p>\r\n<p><img width="970" height="654" src="http://www.jnuae.cn/userfiles/image/%E6%9C%AA%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D3.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<img width="1034" height="592" src="http://www.jnuae.cn/userfiles/image/%E6%9C%AA%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D2.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<img width="990" height="596" src="http://www.jnuae.cn/userfiles/image/%E6%9C%AA%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D.jpg" alt="" /></p>', 10, 1, '2011-08-26 14:00:22'),
(177, 5, '江南大学', '关于2011年江南大学艺术教育专业考试成绩查询通知！', '<p><span style="font-size: large">2011年江南大学艺术教育专业考试成绩查询将于2011.3.15日正式开通，</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: large">届时请广大学生登录网站查询系统查询成绩，并请请考生仔细核对本人信息，</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: large">如有误请拨打0510-85860051。<br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 10, 1, '2011-08-26 14:01:05'),
(178, 5, '江南大学', '著名导演高希希与学院领导亲切会面', '<div style="text-indent: 21.75pt;"><font><font size="2" face="Arial">6月8 日至21日，由国家广电总局和上海市政府主办的第十五届上海电视节、第十二届上海国际电影节在上海举行。期间，著名金牌导演高希希先生、导演、制片人、金 狮奖最佳男主角获得者许文广先生、著名编剧兰晓龙先生与江南大学继续教育学院黄正明院长和殷宝良副院长亲切会面、交谈，并合影留念。</font></font></div>\r\n<div style="text-indent: 21.75pt;"><img width="500" height="375" src="http://www.jnuae.cn/userfiles/10_094127_1.jpg" alt="" /></div>\r\n<div style="text-indent: 21.75pt;"><center><font><font>&nbsp;黄正明院长与高希希导演合影</font></font></center></div>', 11, 1, '2011-08-26 14:03:07'),
(179, 5, '江南大学', '恭喜江南大学艺术教育中心网站开通', '<p><font face="Verdana"><font face="Verdana">恭喜江南大学艺术教育中心网站正式开通!网站的各项功能均已投入正常使用中,欢迎广大师生浏览!</font></font></p>', 12, 1, '2011-08-26 14:05:07'),
(61, 6, '上海交通大学网院', '2011年秋季高升专、高升本招生简章', '<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">上海交通大学是我国历史最悠久的高等学府之一，是教育部直属、教育部与上海市共建的全国重点大学，是国家</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&ldquo;七五&rdquo;、&ldquo;八五&rdquo;重点建设和&ldquo;211工程&rdquo;、&ldquo;985工程&rdquo;的首批建设高校。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">经教育部批准，上海交通大学于</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2000年</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">7 月作为全国现代远程教育试点高校成立了网络教育学院，开展网络教育。为构建终身学习体系，2009年4月，上海交通大学将网络教育学院和成人教育学院合并 为继续教育学院。继续教育学院设立网络教育部，继续举办网络教育。上海交通大学决定2011年继续招收非全日制计划外专科起点本科、高中起点专科网络教育 学生，由网络教育部负责实施教学及管理。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">基于互联网的混合型学习模式</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">实行完全学分制，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">非全日制，走读。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">学生在学习期限内</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">可以按照学院推荐的进度学习，也可以根据个人需求自主制订学习计划</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">，学习形式自主、灵活。&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">上课 </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">学生可就近选择上课教室，也可按规定选择网上实时直播或者非实时点播。&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">考勤 </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">网上考勤与教室电子考勤相结合，全程跟踪学习进程。&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">辅导 </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">阶段性网上辅导&nbsp;+学期考试前集中辅导。&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">考核 </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">传统考试与网上考核相结合。</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">高中起点专科</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">一</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">、招生对象及条件&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">网络高等学历教育是主要面向成人从业人员的非全日制教育。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">高中起点专科考生须持有国民教育系列高中（含中专、中职、技校）或高中以上毕业证书。考生户籍所在地不限。&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">二、招生专业及入学考试科目</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">\r\n<p align="center" style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"> </span></p>\r\n<table style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-table-layout-alt: fixed">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style="HEIGHT: 14.25pt">\r\n            <td width="72" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 54pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">专业分类&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="179" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 134.25pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">招生专业&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="216" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 162pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)" colspan="3">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">入学考试科目</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="HEIGHT: 14.25pt">\r\n            <td width="72" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 54pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">理&nbsp;工&nbsp;类</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="179" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 134.25pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><a title="" href="http://zhaosheng.onlinesjtu.com/zyjs/ShowArticle.asp?ArticleID=63" target="_blank"><font color="#ff0000">计算机科学与技术</font></a>、<a title="" href="http://zhaosheng.onlinesjtu.com/zyjs/ShowArticle.asp?ArticleID=67" target="_blank"><font color="#ff0000">船舶技术</font></a></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="72" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 54pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)" rowspan="4">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">英语</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="72" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 54pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)" rowspan="4">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">综合数学</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="72" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 54pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)" rowspan="4">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">语文</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="HEIGHT: 33.75pt">\r\n            <td width="72" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 54pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">经济管理类</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="179" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 134.25pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt sol