-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><a title="" href="http://zhaosheng.onlinesjtu.com/zyjs/ShowArticle.asp?ArticleID=54" target="_blank"><font color="#ff0000">艺术设计</font></a>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">注：&nbsp;各专业满&nbsp;30人以上方可开班。&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">三、入学考试及免试政策</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">1、考试入学&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;由上海交通大学命题并组织入学测试，择优录取为2011年秋季学生。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(255,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;<font color="#000000">统一入学考试时间：</font><font color="#f73809">2011年8月13日</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(255,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2、单科免试、保送生测试、免试入学政策</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">（一）单科免试</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;年满40周岁者可申请免考入学考试科目&ldquo;英语&rdquo;。&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">（二）保送生测试&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">（1）获得校级及以上优秀奖励者的10、11届中专中职毕业生，可申请面试入学；&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">（2）达到当年成人高考专科控制分数线者，可申请面试入学。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">（三）免试入学&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">获得国民教育系列大学专科及以上毕业证书者，免试入学。&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">四、学习期限、学分、学费</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">实行学分制管理，基本修业年限为两年半至五年，一年两学期，每学期按学分缴纳学费。&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">英语专业总计&nbsp;82学分，每学分&nbsp;200元，每学期按学分缴纳学费；</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">艺术设计专业总计 82学分，每学分 280元，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">每学期按学分缴纳学费；</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">其它专业总计&nbsp;82学分，每学分&nbsp;180元，每学期按学分缴纳学费。&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">五、毕业证书</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;学历教育学生根据有关规定修读完成教学计划规定的学分，成绩合格，可获得上海交通大学毕业证书（注明&nbsp;&ldquo;&nbsp;网络教育&nbsp;&rdquo;&nbsp;），由教育部统一电子注册，国家承认。</span></p>\r\n<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">高中起点本科</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: -21pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 21pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">一、</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">招生对象及条件：</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">同&ldquo;高中起点专科&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: -21pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 21pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">二、</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">招生专业及入学考试科目</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">：</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">招收<a title="" href="http://zhaosheng.onlinesjtu.com/zyjs/ShowArticle.asp?ArticleID=54" target="_blank"><font color="#ff0000">艺术设计</font></a>专业，入学考试科目为语文、英语、专业课。</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">三、</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">入学考试及免试政策：</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">由上海交通大学命题并组织入学测试，择优录取为2011年秋季学生。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 统一入学考试时间：<font color="#f73809">2011年8月13日</font><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(255,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 学院承认2011年全国普通高考、三校生高考成绩，达到学院规定录取分数线者，可申请凭高考成绩免试录取。</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">四、学习期限、学分、学费：</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">实行学分制管理，基本修业年限为五年至七年，一年两学期。</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">总计200学分，每学分280元，每学期按学分缴纳学费。</span></p>\r\n<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">非学历课程进修生</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">１、课程进修生属于非学历教育。凡有能力并自愿参加课程学习的所有人员均可报名参加学习。学历、专业、年龄不限。&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">２、课程进修生入学前可参加我院课程进修生入学测试。&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">３、课程进修生可根据个人需求选修我院开设的所有课程。&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">４、课程进修生按课程管理，申请者每学期必须按规定交纳所修学分的学费，收费标准与学历教育相同。&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">５、课程进修生在取得学历教育资格后，课程进修期间所获学分及课程成绩，可按学院规定申请转入学历教育。最短修业年限自取得学历教育资格后开始计算。&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">奖学金制度</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">学院2011年拨款100万元作为奖学金，分别设立&ldquo;新生奖学金&rdquo;、&ldquo;卓越奖学金&rdquo;和&ldquo;优秀奖学金&rdquo;三类奖项。以鼓励广大学生刻苦学习，自强不息。奖励名额不低于在籍学生的10%，对于成绩突出的学生予以减免学费的高额奖励。奖学金申请网址&nbsp;</span><span><a href="http://scholarship.onlinesjtu.com/"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; TEXT-DECORATION: underline; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">http://scholarship.onlinesjtu.com</span></a></span></p>', 9, 1, '2011-08-15 11:52:21');
INSERT INTO `mbnews` (`nid`, `nclass`, `s_name`, `ntitle`, `ncon`, `nclick`, `nbool`, `ndate`) VALUES
(62, 6, '上海交通大学网院', '2011年秋季第二本科招生简章', '<br />\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">上海交通大学是我国历史最悠久的高等学府之一，是教育部直属、教育部与上海市共建的全国重点大学，是国家</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&ldquo;七五&rdquo;、&ldquo;八五&rdquo;重点建设和&ldquo;211工程&rdquo;、&ldquo;985工程&rdquo;的首批建设高校。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">经教育部批准，上海交通大学于</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2000年</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">7 月作为全国现代远程教育试点高校成立了网络教育学院，开展网络教育。为构建终身学习体系，2009年4月，上海交通大学将网络教育学院和成人教育学院合并 为继续教育学院。继续教育学院设立网络教育部，继续举办网络教育。上海交通大学决定2011年继续招收非全日制计划外第二本科、专科起点本科、高中起点专 科、高中起点本科网络教育学生，由网络教育部负责实施教学及管理。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">基于互联网的混合型学习模式</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">实行完全学分制，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">非全日制，走读。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">学生在学习期限内</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">可以按照学院推荐的进度学习，也可以根据个人需求自主制订学习计划</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">，学习形式自主、灵活。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">上课 </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">学生可就近选择上课教室，也可按规定选择网上实时直播或者非实时点播。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">考勤 </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">网上考勤与教室电子考勤相结合，全程跟踪学习进程。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">辅导 </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">阶段性网上辅导&nbsp;+学期考试前集中辅导。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">考核 </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">传统考试与网上考核相结合。</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 181.5pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">第二本科</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">一、招生对象：</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">已获得国民教育系列大学本科（及以上）毕业证书者。</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">二、招生专业：</span></p>\r\n<table style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse; MARGIN-LEFT: 17.55pt; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-table-layout-alt: fixed">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style="HEIGHT: 11.4pt">\r\n            <td width="93" valign="top" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 70.15pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">专业分类</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="465" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 349.1pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">招生专业</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="HEIGHT: 35.45pt">\r\n            <td width="93" valign="top" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 70.15pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">理工类</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="465" valign="top" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 349.1pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">计算机科学与技术、机械设计制造及其自动化、船舶与海洋工程、电气工程及其自动化</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="HEIGHT: 20pt">\r\n            <td width="93" valign="top" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 70.15pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">经济管理类</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="465" valign="top" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 349.1pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">金融学、会计学、工商管理、人力资源管理、国际经济与贸易、行政管理</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="HEIGHT: 12.05pt">\r\n            <td width="93" valign="top" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 70.15pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">外语类</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="465" valign="top" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 349.1pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">英语（商务）</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="HEIGHT: 12.05pt">\r\n            <td width="93" valign="top" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 70.15pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">艺术类</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="465" valign="top" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 349.1pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">艺术设计</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;注：各专业满&nbsp;30人以上方可开班。</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">三、入学方式：</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">凭本科毕业证书报名，通过审核后免试录取。</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">四、学习期限、学分、学费</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">1、实行学分制管理，基本修业年限为两年半至五年，一年两学期，每学期按学分缴纳学费。</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">2、总学分在60学分左右，各专业具体学分数详见教学计划。</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">3、英语专业每学分200元；艺术设计专业每学分250元；其它专业每学分180元。</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">五、毕业证书、学位证书&nbsp;：</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">同&ldquo;专科起点本科&rdquo;。</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">奖学金制度</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">学院2011年拨款100万元作为奖学金，分别设立&ldquo;新生奖学金&rdquo;、&ldquo;卓越奖学金&rdquo;和&ldquo;优秀奖学金&rdquo;三类奖项。以鼓励广大学生刻苦学习，自强不息。奖励名额不低于在籍学生的10%，对于成绩突出的学生予以减免学费的高额奖励。</span><span><a href="http://scholarship.onlinesjtu.com/"></a></span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 14.75pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">报名方法</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">1、</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">报名需备：</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">（1）本人身份证原件及国民教育系列相应证书原件及复印件，应届毕业生需携带学生证；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">（2）符合科目免试条件者需携带相关证书原件及复印件一份；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">（3）报名时缴纳报名考务费共92元（艺术设计专业报名考务费144元）&nbsp;，报名后一律不退款。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">特别提示</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">◆考生户籍所在地不限，不转户口，不调档案，不享受国家补贴等全日制学生待遇，学院不提供、安排、介绍住宿。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">◆学校将在入学时、学习期间、毕业前多次查验学生的国民教育系列毕业证书及电子注册号，凡持不符合条件的证书或假证报名者，一切后果均自负。一经发现，学校有权取消其报名、学习、毕业资格，且不退还学费。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">◆</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(255,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">学院招生政策包括毕业证书、学位证书颁发以国家现行政策为准，若国家政策调整，即按新政策执行。</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(255,0,0); FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span></p>', 10, 1, '2011-08-15 11:55:07');
INSERT INTO `mbnews` (`nid`, `nclass`, `s_name`, `ntitle`, `ncon`, `nclick`, `nbool`, `ndate`) VALUES
(63, 6, '上海交通大学网院', '2011年秋季艺术设计高升本/专升本招生简章', '<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">一、学院简介</span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><font size="2">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;上海交通大学网络教育自2001年起与上海交通大学媒体与设计学院合作招收艺术设计专业本科生，培养学生向艺术监制、多媒体设计师、展示设计师、平面设计师、包装设计师、企业策划师等应用领域方向发展。此专业历年网络教育全国英语统考，全国排名前三名。</font></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<font size="2">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;奖学金制度：学院2010年拨款100万元作为奖学金，分别设立&ldquo;新生奖学金&rdquo;、&ldquo;卓越奖学金&rdquo;和&ldquo;优秀奖学金&rdquo;三类奖项。以鼓励广大学生刻苦学习，自强不息。奖励名额不低于在籍学生的10%，对于成绩突出的学生予以减免学费的高额奖励。</font><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"> </b></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">二、主要课程设置</span></b></p>\r\n<p><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">\r\n<p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse; MARGIN-LEFT: 34.2pt; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-table-layout-alt: fixed">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style="HEIGHT: 45.85pt">\r\n            <td width="100" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 75.05pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">专业基础课</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="175" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 131.95pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p class="p0" style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">素描、色彩、数字媒体艺术设计、摄影基础、图形与编排设计、创意与策划</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="96" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 72pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">专业方向课</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="204" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 153pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p class="p0" style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">二维动画设计、非线性编辑、企业形象识别、展示设计、包装设计</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="HEIGHT: 17.85pt">\r\n            <td width="100" valign="center" rowspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 75.05pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">选修课</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="175" valign="center" rowspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 131.95pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p class="p0" style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">影视音乐、书籍装帧、</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">DV</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">设计、多媒体设计</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="96" valign="center" rowspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 72pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p class="p0" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">学位课</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="204" valign="bottom" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 153pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p class="p0" style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">艺术设计概论</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="HEIGHT: 13.85pt">\r\n            <td width="204" valign="bottom" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 153pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p class="p0" style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">广告设计</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class="p0" style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n</b></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">三、授课名师，沐浴百年校风</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US"><a target="_blank" href="http://zhaosheng.onlinesjtu.com/zsjz/UploadFiles_5452/201104/20110406001024125.jpg"><img width="134" height="173" border="0" src="http://zhaosheng.onlinesjtu.com/zsjz/UploadFiles_5452/201104/20110406001024125.jpg" alt="" />&nbsp;</a></span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span></span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">顾惠忠（专业主任）副教授</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">/</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">硕士生导师</span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">，现任教育部艺术类教育指导委员会委员；上海工业设计协会副理事长；上海设计中心副主任；上海包装技术协会包装设计专业委员会副主任；中国美术家协会会员；上海美术家协会粉画工作委员会副会长；中国图像图形学会数码艺术委员会委员；《上海包装》编委。</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><img width="120" height="128" border="0" src="http://zhaosheng.onlinesjtu.com/zsjz/UploadFiles_5452/201104/20110406001024520.jpg" alt="" />&nbsp;</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">詹仁左（专业教师）教授</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">/</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">硕士生导师</span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">，上海交通大学美术教研室主任，北京中国书画社研究员，中国书法协会会员。多年来一直致力于中国书法、花鸟创作，曾在美国、德国、日本举办个人画展。其作品多次被政府作为礼品赠送给克林顿、曼德拉、李光耀等外国元首和政要。</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes"><a target="_blank" href="http://zhaosheng.onlinesjtu.com/zsjz/UploadFiles_5452/201104/20110406001024357.png"><img width="120" height="139" border="0" src="http://zhaosheng.onlinesjtu.com/zsjz/UploadFiles_5452/201104/20110406001024357.png" alt="" />&nbsp;</a></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span></span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">周宏教授</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">/</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">硕士生导师</span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">，上海交通大学媒体与设计学院系主任，中国流行色协会理事、国际平面设计社团协会联盟（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">Icograda</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">）团体会员、上海工业设计协会会员、上海设计师协会会员。曾指导学生获得第二届中国大学生广告大赛三等奖，第二届中国大学生广告大赛上海赛区一等奖等多个奖项。</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes"><a target="_blank" href="http://zhaosheng.onlinesjtu.com/zsjz/UploadFiles_5452/201104/20110406001024893.png"><img width="124" height="153" border="0" src="http://zhaosheng.onlinesjtu.com/zsjz/UploadFiles_5452/201104/20110406001024893.png" alt="" />&nbsp;</a>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">孔繁强副教授</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">/</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">硕士生导师</span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">，上海交通大学媒体与设计学院副教授，毕业于上海交通大学设计艺术学硕士、东京艺术大学设计科伊藤隆道空间造型研究室访问学者，中国工业设计协会会员，日本环境艺术学会会员。获上海交通大学优秀教师奖、上海市优秀教学成果奖、上海市优秀教材奖，撰写国家</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">&ldquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">十五</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">重点规划教材。</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><a target="_blank" href="http://zhaosheng.onlinesjtu.com/zsjz/UploadFiles_5452/201104/20110406001025153.png"><img width="124" height="125" border="0" src="http://zhaosheng.onlinesjtu.com/zsjz/UploadFiles_5452/201104/20110406001025153.png" alt="" />&nbsp;</a></span></b></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">邵奇副</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">教授</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">/</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">博士</span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">，曾分别就读于中国电影艺术研究中心、北京电影学院研究生部，获硕士学位，复旦大学新闻学院广播电视系，获博士学位。中国电影家协会理论工作委员会委员，十佳国产电影评委。</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><a target="_blank" href="http://zhaosheng.onlinesjtu.com/zsjz/UploadFiles_5452/201104/20110406001025597.png"><img width="124" height="164" border="0" src="http://zhaosheng.onlinesjtu.com/zsjz/UploadFiles_5452/201104/20110406001025597.png" alt="" />&nbsp;</a></span></b></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">吴正恭</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"> </span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">副教授，硕士生导师</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"> 1985</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">年赴美，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">1990</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">年毕业于美国历史最悠久的宾夕法尼亚美术学院，后移居纽约。作品曾由纽约、洛杉矶和费城的五家最老或最大的（写实）画廊代理，其中包括肖像画行业中在世界上最有影响的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">Portraits, Inc.</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">2003</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">年进入上海交通大学媒体与设计学院，除了美术基础课外，同时开设西洋美术史课程。现为美术专业负责人。</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><a target="_blank" href="http://zhaosheng.onlinesjtu.com/zsjz/UploadFiles_5452/201104/20110406001025718.png"><img width="124" height="156" border="0" src="http://zhaosheng.onlinesjtu.com/zsjz/UploadFiles_5452/201104/20110406001025718.png" alt="" />&nbsp;</a></span></b></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">席涛副</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">教授，硕士生导师</span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">，设计系党支部书记</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"> </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">曾分别就读于江南大学装潢系、东华大学设计艺术学院，获硕士学位。曾赴澳大利亚</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">LA-TRUBE</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">大学研修。亚洲基础造型设计联合会会员、中国工业设计学会会员、上海包装设计协会会员、上海工业设计协会会员。</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; TEXT-INDENT: 9pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><br />\r\n</span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">四、获奖情况</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">名师传道授业，学生硕果累累</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18pt; tab-stops: 18.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">1</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Roman&rsquo;; FONT-SIZE: 7pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体"> </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">上海多媒体形象设计大赛二、三等奖</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18pt; tab-stops: 18.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">2</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Roman&rsquo;; FONT-SIZE: 7pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体"> </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">上海世博会志愿者标志入围奖</span></p>\r\n<