动画大赛优秀</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">flash</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">动画作品奖等</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">五、毕业去向</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">天生我才必有用，名校背景添光彩</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><br />\r\n</span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">就业</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">&mdash;&mdash;</span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">在应届生普遍就业难的形势下，交大网络艺术设计毕业生却由于专业能力强和名校学习经历，受到市场的青睐。历届毕业生就业单位包括</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">eBay</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">易趣、新民晚报、人民美术出版社、上海广电影视制作公司、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">ELLE</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">杂志社、上海盛大网络有限公司、奥创广告等。</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">★</span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">09</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">年毕业生就业去向包括</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">学生：黄同学</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"> </spa