; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">上海交通大学媒体与设计学院多媒体设计硕士</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">英国邓迪大学设计学硕士</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"> </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">等</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">出国</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">&mdash;&mdash;</span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">交大开放的学术思想，名师丰富的海外经历，使不少学生对国外艺术设计领域产生了兴趣。而且学院注重文化课教育，特别是英文课程，为有志于海外求学的学生打下了坚实的语言基础。</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><br />\r\n</span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">六、招生信息</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: red; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">专升本招生</span></b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"> </span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">★</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">　<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">考生户籍不限。</b></span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><br />\r\n</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">★</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">　<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">入学考试：</b></span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><br />\r\n<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">由上海交通大学自主命题并组织考试，择优录取为</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">2010</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">年秋季学生。</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">入学考时间：</span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: red; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">2011</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: red; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">年8月13日</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: red; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></b></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: red; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </span></span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">考试科目：公共英语、大学语文、设计基础</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><br />\r\n</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">★</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">　艺术设计类专业应届毕业生面试入学政策：满足以下条件之一者，可获得面试入学资格：</span></b><span style="COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 10pt"> </span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 17.95pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">1</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">、取得大学英语四级</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">(CET4)</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">、全国公共英语</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">(PETS</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">）三级或专科英语应用能力</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">B</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">级考试合格证书及上级别证书者；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">2</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">、专科阶段各科平均成绩达</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 10pt"> 70</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">分，英语平均成绩</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">65</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">分及以上者；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">3</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">、获得校级以上优秀奖励者。</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">★</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">　艺术设计类专业毕业生免试政策：具体办法请向报名处咨询。</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">★</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">　<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">学习模式：</b></span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span><span style="COLOR: red"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">专业课双休日教室面授，其余课程提供面授和网络点播两种学习方式。学生可根据需求自由选择。</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">★ </span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">学习期限、学分与学费：</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><br />\r\n</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">实行学分制管理，基本修业年限为两年半至五年，一年两学期，每学期按学分缴纳学费，总计</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">98</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">学分，每学分</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">250</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">元。</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: red; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">10</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: red; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">秋专升本新增专业方向</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: red; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">艺术设计<span lang="EN-US">(</span>珠宝设计与鉴定<span lang="EN-US">)</span></span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt"> </span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">专业介绍<span lang="EN-US"><br />\r\n</span></span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">上海交通大学珠宝专业创办于<span lang="EN-US">1993</span>年， 是上海市最早开办珠宝专业的高等院校，专业特色明显，专业课开设面广，在业界具有广泛的影响力。本专业主要培养珠宝首饰设计、珠宝玉石的鉴定、珠宝首饰评 估及商贸等领域的高级人才。学生通过理论与实践相结合的学习，一般能达到直接为企事业单位服务的目的。近年来，上海交通大学又专门成立了珠宝时尚产业研究 中心，依托媒体与设计学院的设计优势以及国际合作的优势，全面提升珠宝时尚创意技术的研发，促进交叉学科的建设，加速珠宝和创意产业高级人才的培养。</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">学习模式：专业课双休日教室面授，其余课程提供面授和网络点播两种学习方式。学生可根据需求自由选择。</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">就业方向<span lang="EN-US"><br />\r\n</span></span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">主要可进入的工作岗位有：<span lang="EN-US">1</span>、国内外各类珠宝企业中的珠宝首饰设计师、珠宝玉石鉴定及检验人员、贸易及管理人员；<span lang="EN-US">2</span>、珠宝玉石检测鉴定机构；<span lang="EN-US">3</span>、典当企业；<span lang="EN-US">4</span>、拍卖企业；<span lang="EN-US">5</span>、价值评估企业；<span lang="EN-US">6</span>、司法鉴定单位；<span lang="EN-US">7</span>、研究院所；<span lang="EN-US">8</span>、教育培训机构等。</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><br />\r\n</span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">师资介绍</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><br />\r\n</span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">施健</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">副教授</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">/</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">硕士生导师</span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">，现任上海交通大学珠宝时尚产业研究中心执行主任；国家（注册）珠宝玉石质量检验师；全国首饰标准化技术委员会（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">SAC/TC256</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">）观察员；国际（注册）首席珠宝评估师。主编有《珠宝首饰检验》、《珠宝首饰检验与评估》等多部教学书籍，负责制定</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">&ldquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">贵金属、钻石、宝玉石检验员</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">国家职业资格标准及规范。承担过多项省部级宝石类科学研究项目，并获上海市科技进步三等奖。获</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">&ldquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">上海市育才奖</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">&ldquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">上海交通大学优秀教师奖</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">等。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><br />\r\n</span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">傅炯</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">副教授</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">/</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">硕士生导师，</span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">现任上海交通大学媒体与设计学院工业设计专业主任；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">主要从事消费趋势、色彩趋势、设计趋势等方面的研究。发表有《产品流行色基本原理和研究方法》，《当代亚洲色彩应用》，《手工工艺和工艺美术的未来在于发展》等论著。承担过多项产品设计及趋势分析的项目研究。获上海交通大学</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">&ldquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">三育人</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">教学优秀个人称号。</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">李桑</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">上海交通大学珠宝时尚产业研究中心特聘教师，</span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">毕业于上海大学美术学院首饰艺术专业硕士，本科毕业于中国美术学院。曾有多年本科教学和公司工作经验，并在美国游过学，具有良好的英语水平和沟通能力。擅长首饰制作和设计，作品《雪》获</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">2009</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年第十一届全国美展艺术设计类提名奖，为此次美展里仅有的四个获首饰专业奖项中的一个。</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">主要课程设置：</span></b></p>\r\n<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" class="MsoNormalTable" style="MARGIN: auto auto auto 28.8pt; BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse; mso-table-layout-alt: fixed; mso-padding-alt: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style="HEIGHT: 45.85pt">\r\n            <td width="100" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: black 1pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 75.05pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; HEIGHT: 45.85pt; BORDER-TOP: black 1pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-border-alt: solid black .5pt">\r\n            <p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">专业基础课</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="176" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: #f2f2f2; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 131.95pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; HEIGHT: 45.85pt; BORDER-TOP: black 1pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-border-left-alt: solid black .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid black .5pt">\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">设计素描、色彩学、计算机辅助设计、图形与图案设计</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="96" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: #f2f2f2; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 72pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; HEIGHT: 45.85pt; BORDER-TOP: black 1pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-border-left-alt: solid black .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid black .5pt">\r\n            <p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">专业方向课</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="204" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: #f2f2f2; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 153pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; HEIGHT: 45.85pt; BORDER-TOP: black 1pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-border-left-alt: solid black .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid black .5pt">\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">宝石学基础、首饰与时尚设计、首饰制作工艺、宝玉石鉴定、珠宝首饰评估</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="HEIGHT: 17.85pt">\r\n            <td width="100" rowspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: black 1pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 75.05pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; HEIGHT: 17.85pt; BORDER-TOP: #f2f2f2; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-border-top-alt: solid black .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid black .5pt">\r\n            <p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">选修课</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="176" rowspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: #f2f2f2; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 131.95pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; HEIGHT: 17.85pt; BORDER-TOP: #f2f2f2; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-border-left-alt: solid black .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid black .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid black .5pt">\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">市场营销学、摄影基础、中国书画、艺术品鉴赏、专题讲座</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="96" rowspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: #f2f2f2; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 72pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; HEIGHT: 17.85pt; BORDER-TOP: #f2f2f2; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-border-left-alt: solid black .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid black .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid black .5pt">\r\n            <p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">学位课</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="204" valign="bottom" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: #f2f2f2; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 153pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; HEIGHT: 17.85pt; BORDER-TOP: #f2f2f2; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-border-left-alt: solid black .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid black .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid black .5pt">\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">艺术设计概论</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style="HEIGHT: 13.85pt; mso-yfti-lastrow: yes">\r\n            <td width="204" valign="bottom" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: #f2f2f2; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 153pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; HEIGHT: 13.85pt; BORDER-TOP: #f2f2f2; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-border-left-alt: solid black .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid black .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid black .5pt">\r\n            <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">专业设计</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US"><br />\r\n<br style="mso-special-character: line-break" />\r\n<br style="mso-special-character: line-break" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: red; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">高升本招生</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">★</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">　<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">招生对象：国民教育系列的高中（含三校）</b></span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">★</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">　<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">入学考试科目：语文、英语、专业课（素描、色彩、速写）</b></span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">★</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">　<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">命题及录取方式：入学考试由上海交通大学自主命题并组织考试，择优录取。</b></span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">★</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">　<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">免试政策<span lang="EN-US">:</span>学院承认<span lang="EN-US">2011</span>年全国及上海市普通高考成绩、上海市三校生高考、全国及上海市美术类专业统考成绩，达到学院分数者，可申请凭高考成绩免试入学。</b></span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">★</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">　<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">入学考时间：</b></span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: red; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">2011</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: red; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">年8月13日</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: red; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span></b></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: red; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </span></span></b></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><font color="#000000">★&nbsp; 学习模式：课程提供白天教室面授的学习方式<br />\r\n</font></span></b></b></p>\r\n<p><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><font color="#000000">★&nbsp; 学习期限、学分与学费：实行学分管理，基本修业年限为五至六年，一年两学期。每学期学费7000元，总计200学分，每学分280元。</font></span></b></p>\r\n</b></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">★</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">　<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">毕业证书、学位证书：</b></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"> </span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><br />\r\n</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">学历教育学生根据有关规定修读完成教学计划规定的学分，成绩合格，通过全国网络教育</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"> </span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">&ldquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">大学英语<span lang="EN-US">&rdquo;</span>及<span lang="EN-US">&ldquo;</span>计算机应用基础<span lang="EN-US">&rdquo;</span>统一考试，可获得上海交通大学毕业证书（注明</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"> </span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">&ldquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">网络教育<span lang="EN-US">&rdquo;</span>），由教育部统一电子注册，国家承认；符合学位条例规定条件者，授予上海交通大学成人高等教育学士学位。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><a href="http://zhaosheng.onlinesjtu.com/html/zhengshu.html"></a></span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><br style="mso-special-character: line-break" />\r\n<br style="mso-special-character: line-break" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">非学历课程进修生</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">１、课程进修生属于非学历教育。凡有能力并自愿参加课程学习的所有人员均可报名参加学习。学历、专业、年龄不限。</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">２、课程进修生入学前可参加我院课程进修生入学测试。</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">３、课程进修生可根据个人需求选修我院开设的所有课程。</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">４、课程进修生按课程管理，申请者每学期必须按规定交纳所修学分的学费，收费标准与学历教育相同。</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">５、课程进修生在取得学历教育资格后，课程进修期间所获学分及课程成绩，可按学院规定申请转入学历教育。最短修业年限自取得学历教育资格后开始计算。</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="LINE-HEIGHT: 125%; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">七、报名方法</span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><br />\r\n1</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">、报名需备：</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">1</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">）本人身份证原件；（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">2</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">）毕业证书原件（如已通过英语</span></p>', 15, 1, '2011-08-15 11:55:46');
INSERT INTO `mbnews` (`nid`, `nclass`, `s_name`, `ntitle`, `ncon`, `nclick`, `nbool`, `ndate`) VALUES
(64, 6, '上海交通大学网院', '2011年秋季校外学习中心招生简章', '<p>&nbsp; 上海交通大学是我国历史最悠久的高等学府之一，是教育部直属、教育部与上海市共建的全国重点大学，是国家 &ldquo;七五&rdquo;、&ldquo;八五&rdquo;重点建设和&ldquo;211工程&rdquo;、&ldquo;985工程&rdquo;的首批建设高校。 <br />\r\n&nbsp; <br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  经教育部批准，上海交通大学于 2000年  7月作为全国现代远程教育试点高校成立了网络教育学院，开展网络教育。为构建终身学习体系，2009年4月，上海交通大学将网络教育学院和成人教育学院合 并为继续教育学院。继续教育学院设立网络教育部，继续举办网络教育。上海交通大学决定2010年继续招收非全日制计划外专科起点本科、高中起点专科网络教 育学生，由网络教育部负责实施教学及管理。 <br />\r\n&nbsp; <br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>基于互联网的混合型学习模式</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  实行完全学分制，非全日制，走读。学生在学习期限内可以按照学院推荐的进度学习，也可以根据个人需求自主制订学习计划，学习形式自主、灵活。  上课学生可就近选择上课教室，也可按规定选择网上实时直播或者非实时点播。 考勤网上考勤与教室电子考勤相结合，全程跟踪学习进程。 辅导阶段性网上辅导  +学期考试前集中辅导。 考核传统考试与网上考核相结合。</p>\r\n<p align="center"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>高中起点专科</strong></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n一、招生对象及条件 <br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 网络高等学历教育是主要面向成人从业人员的非全日制教育。&nbsp;&nbsp; 高中起点专科考生须持有国民教育系列高中（含中专、中职、技校）或高中以上毕业证书。考生户籍所在地不限。<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n二、招生专业及入学考试科目</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse; MARGIN-LEFT: 24.15pt; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-table-layout-alt: fixed">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="96" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; BORDER-LEFT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0.75pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0.75pt; WIDTH: 72pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0.75pt; BORDER-TOP: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; PADDING-TOP: 0.75pt; mso-border-left-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-right-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(64,64,64); FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">专业分类</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman''; FONT-SIZE: 9pt">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="323" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0.75pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0.75pt; WIDTH: 242.85pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0.75pt; BORDER-TOP: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; PADDING-TOP: 0.75pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(64,64,64); FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">招生专业</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman''; FONT-SIZE: 9pt">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="156" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0.75pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0.75pt; WIDTH: 117.15pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0.75pt; BORDER-TOP: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; PADDING-TOP: 0.75pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0)" colspan="3">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(64,64,64); FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">入学考试科目</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="96" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; BORDER-LEFT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0.75pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0.75pt; WIDTH: 72pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0.75pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; PADDING-TOP: 0.75pt; mso-border-left-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-right-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(64,64,64); FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">理&nbsp;工&nbsp;类</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="323" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0.75pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0.75pt; WIDTH: 242.85pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0.75pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; PADDING-TOP: 0.75pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(64,64,64); FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">计算机科学与技术、船舶技术</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="36" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0.75pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0.75pt; WIDTH: 27.15pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0.75pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; PADDING-TOP: 0.75pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: none; mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0)" rowspan="3">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(64,64,64); FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">英语</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="72" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0.75pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0.75pt; WIDTH: 54pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0.75pt; BORDER-TOP: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; PADDING-TOP: 0.75pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0)" rowspan="3">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(64,64,64); FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">综合数学</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="48" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0.75pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0.75pt; WIDTH: 36pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0.75pt; BORDER-TOP: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; PADDING-TOP: 0.75pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0)" rowspan="3">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(64,64,64); FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">语文</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="96" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; BORDER-LEFT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0.75pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0.75pt; WIDTH: 72pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0.75pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; PADDING-TOP: 0.75pt; mso-border-left-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-right-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(64,64,64); FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">经济管理类</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="323" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0.75pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0.75pt; WIDTH: 242.85pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0.75pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; PADDING-TOP: 0.75pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(64,64,64); FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">国际贸易、会计学、人力资源管理、工商管理、市场营销、国际物流、行政管理</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="96" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; BORDER-LEFT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0.75pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0.75pt; WIDTH: 72pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0.75pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; PADDING-TOP: 0.75pt; mso-border-left-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-right-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(64,64,64); FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">外&nbsp;语&nbsp;类</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="323" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0.75pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0.75pt; WIDTH: 242.85pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 0.75pt; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.75pt inset; PADDING-TOP: 0.75pt; mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.7500pt inset rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(64,64,64); FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">英语（商务）</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">注： 各专业满 30人以上方可开班。 <br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n三、入学考试及免试政策</span></p>\r\n<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">1、考试入学 由上海交通大学命题并组织入学测试，择优录取为2010年秋季学生。</span></p>\r\n<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 入学考时间：<font color="#ee1111">2011年8月13日</font></span></p>\r\n<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;2、单科免试、面试入学、免试入学政策（一）单科免试&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 年满40周岁者可申请免考入学考试科目&ldquo;英语&rdquo;。<br />\r\n（二）面试入学<br />\r\n（1）获得校级及以上优秀奖励者的09、10届中专中职毕业生，可申请面试入学；<br />\r\n（2）达到当年成人高考专科控制分数线者，可申请面试入学。（二）免试入学<br />\r\n&nbsp;获得国民教育系列大学专科及以上毕业证书者，免试入学。<br />\r\n（三）学院承认09年全国及上海市普通高考，上海市三校生高考成绩，达到学院分数线者可申请凭高考成绩免试入学。 <br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;四、学习期限、学分、学费实行学分制管理，基本修业年限为两年半至五年，一年两学期。 课程总学分82学分，每学期按学分缴纳学费。各教学站学费标准请咨询当地教学站。<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n五、毕业证书&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 学历教育学生根据有关规定修读完成教学计划规定的学分，成绩合格，可获得上海交通大学毕业证书（注明 &ldquo;网络教育 &rdquo;），由教育部统一电子注册，国家承认。</span></p>\r\n<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="center" style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>专科起点本科<br />\r\n</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n一、招生对象及条件<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 网络高等学历教育是主要面向成人从业人员的非全日制教育。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 专科起点本科考生须持有国民教育系列大专（含高职）或大专以上毕业证书。考生户籍所在地不限。</span></p>\r\n<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman''; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">二、招生专业及入学考试科目</span></p>\r\n<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse; MARGIN-LEFT: 12.15pt; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-table-layout-alt: fixed">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width="91" valign="top" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 68.4pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0pt; mso-border-left-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)">\r\n            <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ''宋体''; COLOR: rgb(64,64,64); FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">专业分类</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width="216" valign="center" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDIN